cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the segmentation of abdominal organs from medical images using deep learning techniques. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of adversarial networks also suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper deals with medical imaging, which could also place it under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of auto-context for multi-level segmentation refinement suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under neural networks (cs.NE).
